Package com.redis.foundation.ds

Class DSCriterion

java.lang.Object
com.redis.foundation.ds.DSCriterion
public class DSCriterion extends Object
A DSCriterion is responsible for encapsulating a query item, its operator and one or more values. It is exclusively referenced from within a DSCriteria object.
Since:
1.0
Author:
Al Cole

      public void setDataFormat(String aDataFormat)
